<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>x_463716_dlh_pd_goal</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="x_463716_dlh_pd_goal">stateCHANGESTO3^actually_acquired_skillsISNOTEMPTY^EQ<item display_value="Closed Complete" endquery="false" field="state" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="CHANGESTO" or="false" value="3"/><item endquery="false" field="actually_acquired_skills" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="ISNOTEMPTY" or="false" value=""/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>create skill record</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {
    // Add your code here
    var userName = current.opened_by;
    var skills = current.actually_acquired_skills;
    var separatedSkills = skills.toString().split(',');
    for (var i = 0; i < separatedSkills.length; i++) {
        var userSkills = new GlideRecord('sys_user_has_skill');
        userSkills.initialize();
        userSkills.skill = separatedSkills[i];
        userSkills.user = userName;
        userSkills.insert();
        gs.addInfoMessage("New skill record is created");
    }
})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>teodora.radeva</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2022-03-30 10:44:22</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>8bd9d72d07ae8110d44bf16c7c1ed039</sys_id><sys_mod_count>28</sys_mod_count><sys_name>create skill record</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_8bd9d72d07ae8110d44bf16c7c1ed039</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>teodora.radeva</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2022-03-31 07:01:23</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=8bd9d72d07ae8110d44bf16c7c1ed039"/></record_update>
